title: DS210.21 Multi-Datacenter Concepts | Operations with Apache Cassandra
description:
#DataStaxAcademy #DS210
DS210.21 MULTI-DATACENTER CONCEPTS
In this unit, we discuss some multi datacenter concepts around Apache Cassandra and DataStax Enterprise. Multi datacenter is one of the neatest features of Apache Cassandra.

LEARN FOR FREE at https://academy.datastax.com -- access all the FREE complete courses, tutorials, and hands-on exercises.

ASK QUESTIONS at https://community.datastax.com -- where experts from DataStax & the Apache Cassandra community share their expertise everyday.
